| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1948 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: edbd7fcf-229a-5392-8c30-d2aab6ea10e5"
